---
title: Premium Roast Beef & Gravy for Dinner with Chocolate Toffee Pudding & Poached Pears for Dessert
description: Cosy up to a slightly fancier version of home-cooking with this succulent and mouth-watering premium steak. Paired with a
creamy rosemary mash and pan-seared baby broccoli, then topped with crispy bits of bacon, this dish will make you fall in love
with the classic Sunday roast all over again. For an added slice of heaven, dig into decadent chocolate toffee pudding for dessert!

